{"tid":2478652,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國快槍俠難忍色慾 把狗狗帶到籠內性侵2分鐘","createTime":"2021-04-07T08:25:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T08:40:19.000Z","uid":276273,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fee7eb7299ab24404d43c81760a321ffb627dd26","tid":2478652,"uid":276273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:25:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3491677\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3491677&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtCcuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=985a600c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3491677&h=f4251895\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3491677</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國微博近日流傳一起男子性侵狗的事件，一名男子引誘狗狗進狗籠並對牠性侵，過程約莫兩分鐘。<br />\n微博上流傳的畫面顯示，中國4日中午，一名男子騎車時看到路邊有一隻大黃狗，他突然色心大起，覺得這隻大黃狗有著強烈的誘惑，竟然拿出食物引誘狗狗，接著摸牠的臀部、下體，男子這樣還不滿足，直接把狗狗帶進籠內對牠性侵，完事後一人一狗走出狗籠，各自離去，歷時約莫2分鐘。<br />\n這起事件讓網友們相當傻眼，直呼狗狗真可憐，目前未能得知事發地點與男子身分。"},{"pid":"effd99975076670e89f2f8d21b45667c078ca401","tid":2478652,"uid":194376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:30:05.000Z","msg":"片呢"},{"pid":"64895fe1853f9b576af29ea4abfe1a2485786781","tid":2478652,"uid":229633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:31:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0dfc0ac16f4b273b1a542f841f6b3f728f7c180","tid":2478652,"uid":277031,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:31:39.000Z","msg":"完事後一人一狗走出狗籠，各自離去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a250c87adb27e9774867a43f65e6db842ebff5","tid":2478652,"uid":69841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04